Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大伙儿 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好困…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 葛城姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每日清晨一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样飞鸟就能精神满满啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别搞什么奇怪的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.30,Comment,,0,0,0,,而且想睡的是葛城姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天又是一个好天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&H211714&}傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&H626466&}傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&H303135&}傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&HD2C1CB&}傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\blur5\3c&HAEA7D1&}傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即是受操控的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}亦称作傀垒 木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fs36\pos(654,650)}KAIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fs36\pos(764,650)}DEKU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：即为傀儡的另外两种读法 DEKU汉字写作木偶 KUGUTSU与KAIRAI相同皆为傀儡 中文取意译
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外 也指自由自在地操纵傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}进而戏弄对手于鼓掌之间的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听你们说来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}袭击你们的应该是一位忍术高超的傀儡使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&H211714&}傀儡使？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&HA0E2EE&}傀儡使？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&H626466&}傀儡使？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&HD2C1CB&}傀儡使？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\3c&HAEA7D1&}傀儡使？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…有话想说请一个人代表就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请问那位傀儡使的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在还没办法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.79,Comment,,0,0,0,,讨厌…葛城姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但愿不会有什么灾厄降临
Comment: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:39.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校準幀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:46.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:05.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:08.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}闇雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:15.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:26.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:33.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:39.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:52.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:57.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON’T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:46.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:05.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:08.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.47,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:15.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:26.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:33.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:39.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.87,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:52.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:57.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
